# PHPUnit Dojo extension

This extension feeds the backend of your choice with events, to gather statistics about the session.

## How to start

1. install the dependency :

`composer require akenlab/phpunit-dojo-extension`

2. register the listener in your phpunit.xml :

```
...
<listeners>
    <listener class="Akenlab\DojoExtension\DojoListener">
        <arguments>
            <object class="Akenlab\DojoExtension\DojoAgent">
                <arguments>
                    <object class="Akenlab\DojoExtension\Drivers\ConsoleDriver" />
                </arguments>
            </object>
        </arguments>
    </listener>
</listeners>
...
```
